findings.title: Owner can change the tax and liquidity fee
findings.description: The owner has the privilege to modify the tax and liquidity fee.

findings.title: Owner can change the maximum transaction amount
findings.description: The owner has the privilege to modify the maximum allowed transaction amount.

findings.title: Owner can exclude from the fee
findings.description: The owner has the privilege to exclude addresses from the fee.

findings.title: Owner can exclude from and include in bots array
findings.description: The owner has privileges to modify the bots array, which could lead to potential security issues.

findings.title: Owner can change number of tokens to sell to add to liquidity
findings.description: The owner has the privilege to modify the number of tokens sold to add liquidity, which may lead to potential security risks.

findings.title: Owner can claim all tokens from the contract
findings.description: The owner has the privilege to claim all tokens from the contract without any restrictions.

findings.title: Liquidity Address Can Manually Send BNBs to Liquidity Address
findings.description: The liquidity address has the capability to manually send BNBs to itself.

findings.title: Owner can lock and unlock
findings.description: The owner has the privilege to lock and unlock, which could allow them to retake privileges even after ownership was renounced.

findings.title: DoS with block gas limit
findings.description: The contract may be vulnerable to Denial of Service (DoS) attacks due to the block gas limit.

findings.title: Out of gas exception if there will be a long excluded addresses list in includeInReward() function
findings.description: The function includeInReward() uses a loop to find and remove addresses from the _excluded list, which can cause an OUT_OF_GAS exception if the excluded addresses list is too long.

findings.title: Out of gas exception if there will be a long excluded addresses list in _getCurrentSupply function
findings.description: The function _getCurrentSupply uses a loop to evaluate total supply and could be aborted with OUT_OF_GAS exception if there is a long excluded addresses list.
